410	     * Both indexes (`individuals`, `groups`) are populated in a single pass
411	     * and kept in sync.
412	     *
413	     * @param lineItems - The receipt's line items with their assignments.
414	     * @returns An {@link ItemSplits} graph ready to hand to the total calculators.
415	     *
